client.gui.marketingmanager

Class DeterminingFuelRatesController

  • java.lang.Object
    • client.gui.marketingmanager.DeterminingFuelRatesController

  • public class DeterminingFuelRatesController
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is the gui class of Determining fuel Rates controller. this class will show to the marketing manager the current and max fuel rates and will allow him/her to make a request to change new fuel rate, the request will be sended to the ceo of the company.
    Version:
    final
    Author:
    Barak and Or Yom Tov
